Use case label: UC09.01.02
Use Story: US09.01.02
Test case: testPushTradeOnline() in testOffline.java
Participating actor: Borrower
Goal : Be able to make trades while offline, and push application and expense information online once get connectivity.
Tigger : Borrower makes a trade while offline and then gets an online connection.
Precondition: Borrower proposed a new trade with a seleted friend
Postcondition: Trades are pushed
Basic Flow:
    Borrower proposed a new trade with a selected friend
    System pushes trade online as soon as it gets connectivity
